{
  "stem": "15943.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they sung and recited German classics in a much nicer German than those guards spoke.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Ana, or Arztin, now, doctor, had asked me-- I was still in the sick room-- asked me to come and to recite some of the poems.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I recited '[NON-ENGLISH],' which means the underground shelter in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the guards understood what I said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I talked about what they're doing to us, all those horrible things that are happening.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the day will come we'll take revenge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the guards looked at the commandant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She knew what I was saying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she just ignored it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I remember the girls turning white because they knew there's the punishment here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then I recited another poem, 'A Message to Mama,' '[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].' Using the clouds as messages, I send a message of hope because I held onto that hope that she's alive.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that what kept me going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother's legacy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even as a child, I remember when things were tough-- and I'm sure things were tough quite often, but I did not realize it-- she said that as long as there's life, there is hope.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As long as there is a pulse beating-- we had all different version of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where there's life, there's hope-- basically all come from the same stem, from, from, from the same root.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she would always use that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And many times when I was feeling there's no reason to go on, I remembered what she said.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As long as there's life, there is hope.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that-- after I finished reading the poem, 'A Message to Mama,' I fainted.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took me back to the sick room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this vicious commandant chased after me.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
